text: Lypsimena proletaria is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Melzer in 1931. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Lypsimena proletaria. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1931
